#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:2
#: 263168d87a6d41a392c73314f4f21767
msgid "安全"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:17
#: 806c684fb4e8404eacd1d759eb122ab6
msgid "ESP8266 的固件是否能被读取？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:19
#: 5aa3b4b675e44ec0976dd0d4a6b9b017
msgid "ESP8266 固件由于放置在外部 flash, 数据可被外部读取。并且 ESP8266 不支持 flash 加密，所有数据均为明文。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:24
#: e875d268f953475296a1af28fca7d796
msgid "ESP8285 是否可以固件加密？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:26
#: d126222b9a2a4f1dba4c36ae2e2e2002
msgid "ESP8285 芯片自身未有固件加密功能，无法完成固件加密。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:27
#: 25611b4b3cdd46898f8f0919a1131e6b
msgid "ESP32 以及 ESP32-S2 芯片都有具备固件加密功能。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:28
#: 04d04fc6dd4d48b28962abf5f970987b
msgid "也可选择外置加密芯片来完成部分数据加密。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:33
#: aad87255cdad444ab50a266dc11b5ee7
msgid "开启 security boot 后, 编译报错缺少文件 ？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:35
#: b70b6e448c4544d595f9506c06be4d77
msgid ""
"错误 log：/d/ESP32/esp-mdf/esp-"
"idf/components/bootloader_support/Makefile.projbuild:7：/f/ESP32Root/secure_boot_signing_key.pem。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:37
#: 5a0e6a549c294eadb001bac3b06688fc
msgid ""
"报错原因 security boot 是固件签名校验的功能，该功能需要生成证书对。相关资料 `参考 "
"<https://blog.csdn.net/espressif/article/details/79362094>`_。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:42
#: af63d7c2ad424bf49c92d75c7a5fd911
msgid "模组使能 Secure boot 是否可以再次烧录 ？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:44
#: 4cad55ff0bd44bcf97657b3631349368
msgid "Secure boot 配置为 One-time，那么就只能烧录一次，不可以再重新 烧录 bootloader 固件。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:45
#: 81a2bb4016494084b1a1941d6aa41937
msgid "Secure boot 配置为 Reflashable, 可以重新烧录 bootloader 固件。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:50
#: fe3a8871eed04b038d01d5dd0ed19b9a
msgid "模组使能 flash encrypted, 重新烧录后出现 ``flash read error`` 错误 ？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:52
#: 5a715004bec44baf96381971ea470ecf
msgid "模组使能 flash encrypted, 重新烧录后，发现会出现 flash read error 的现象."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:54
#: 079c893347ea4f1381a8a62316792fc7
msgid ""
"模组使能 flash encrypted 后，模组开启加密功能后将不支持明文固件烧录。可以通过 espefuse.py "
"脚本将加密关闭后再次烧录，或者已知密钥烧录密文。注意: flash encrypted 加密开关存在次数，仅可重复 3 次。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:59
#: d20f2ff807e7431291dc991e4d6655c1
msgid "ESP32 打开 flash 加密和 secure boot 后，如何关闭？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:61
#: 8b8de4fcca804c00bc9faee3543f6a37
msgid "如果您使用的是 one-time flash（Release） 模式，那么 flash 加密和 secure boot 都是不能关闭的。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:62
#: 9c61805b1a8b41be802d4ab96bef8b7a
msgid ""
"如果您使用的是 reflashable （Development(NOT SECURE)）模式，那么 `flash 加密 "
"<https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/release-v4.1/security"
"/flash-encryption.html#disabling-flash-encryption>`_ 可以关闭，secure boot "
"不能关闭。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:67
#: 48fc872676204b97af559099e7d9e604
msgid "ESP32 保护固件安全的方式有那些？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:69
#: de1db49771144f6eb3a11e1d13b0752d
msgid "ESP32 支持 flash encryption 与 secure boot."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:70
#: c98dfc7df3434ec9a44d6c0923e26f96
msgid ""
"Flash 加密参考文档：`flash encryption <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-"
"idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/security/flash-encryption.html>`_，"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:71
#: 40abac1b7740405d9f5267827bf0c31b
msgid ""
"安全引导参考文档： `secure boot <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-"
"idf/en/latest/esp32/security/secure-boot-v1.html>`_，"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:72
#: ea3d7db6117c4eef9543e42c8201e3f3
msgid ""
"安全引导 V2 参考文档：`ECO3 Chip secure boot V2 "
"<https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/security"
"/secure-boot-v2.html>`_。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:77
#: e170e5722c244e12b20398800983b856
msgid "ESP32 启动 Flash 加密后进行 GDB 调试，为何会不断复位重启？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:79
#: 9c95a4e3c67044c9944a0ea7b3b5fffb
msgid ""
"ESP32 启动了 Flash 加密或 Secure Boot 默认将会禁用 JTAG 调试，请参见说明 `JTAG with Flash "
"Encryption <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-"
"idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-guides/jtag-debugging/tips-and-quirks.html"
"#jtag-with-flash-encryption-or-secure-boot>`_。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/security.rst:80
#: 79c323c5d5484c7d8447c168f8ef1dd6
msgid "可以通过 esptool 工具包中的 espefuse.py summary 脚本指令读取当前芯片 JTAG 状态。"
msgstr ""

